  "Say": {
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Suspicious people? Yes, I did see them. It was right around the time Tae Sang came to inspect the trees."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "The Peach Monkeys and Reindeer were in a tizzy when that group passed through. I've never seen them so worked up. I fear they're becoming a threat to the farm."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "If they don't settle down, this year's harvest will be ruined. They must learn discipline! Can you teach them?"
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirType": "sub"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "Give them a good wallop! I want to see some monkey fur on you when you return."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "I guess you're making the right decision. These majestic trees DO deserve to die at the hands of a feral monkey colony, don't they?"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "How's the Peach Monkey and Reindeer situation?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "That was brilliant. They're as docile as can be now. This year will bring a magnificent harvest after all."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "What motivation do your enemies have for ruining my precious peaches? There must be something for them to gain."
        }
      },
